Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}堅強的內心充滿推理的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}永遠以最敏銳的節奏揭開案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}再次登場的警視廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}一起探索不自然的案件和過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}看上去是小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}他的名字就是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.61,0:01:51.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你還在家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k107}是我啦 剛才真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}我手機的電池好像用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.03,0:02:02.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}我好不容易找到公用電話才下車打給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看看 我應該再過30分鐘就會到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好 那我們一會兒見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:35.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被封印的目暮的秘密(前編)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這件怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是送給京極先生的禮物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}好像太可愛點了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.95,0:02:51.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}我倒覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k245}這種樣式單純的毛衣會比較適合他那一型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不行啦 要手織的才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為什麼非要手織的不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.42,0:03:01.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k263}園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}手織的毛衣穿起來會比較暖和罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}妳還想唬我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.05,0:03:15.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k193}因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k117}我在上次寄給他的信裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k139}無意中提到了一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.95,0:03:23.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}我正在為我喜歡的人織毛衣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.75,0:03:27.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 我又很清楚自己不是很有耐性的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.76,0:03:28.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}所以你才想買現成的手織毛衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.97,0:03:34.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}當成你自己織的送給他當作禮物是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.55,0:03:39.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}因為我實在是找不到臺階下了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k123}看在你對自己喜歡的人勇敢表白的份上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我就不掀妳的底牌了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.84,0:03:49.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}可是 我到現在都還沒有對阿真說我喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}妳不是已經在信上寫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}妳正在為喜歡的人織毛衣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.06,0:03:55.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}妳這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.48,0:03:59.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k42}要是京極先生誤會妳另有喜歡的人要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說對了 這就是我的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他這樣想的時候 心裏一定會忐忑不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這時我寄包裹給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他一定會奇怪 園子怎麼會寄包裹給我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就在他納悶的時候 打開包裹一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.34,0:04:23.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}發現我原來是在為他織毛衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.17,0:04:27.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這就是我精心設計的愛情大作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}聽妳在這裏一廂情願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}他要放棄妳了我可不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.88,0:04:34.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}阿真這個人比較沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k171}我如果不這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}根本就不知道他心裡是怎麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}雖然我知道他很在意我 但僅僅這樣還不夠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是人家又沒有勇氣去直接問他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:52.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}那蘭妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.02,0:04:57.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k112}妳可又知道 新一那傢伙的心裏是怎麼看待妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:04:59.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k104}看吧 看吧 我就說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:03.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k135}其實你也很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k145}妳也很想問 到底是不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就以青梅竹馬而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}說我不在意這件事是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.29,0:05:15.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.88,0:05:20.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k159}可是 可是可是可是可是可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}明明心裡想問 卻又不敢問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我現在就是這種心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你老實交代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k97}妳是不是常常做這種白日夢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我才沒有想過這些呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}那 蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}我想到停車場去找叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}我陪他一起等你們好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那你轉告爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k113}讓他先到百貨公司裏面的通心麵館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}我們買好了就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}蘭 這件好不好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.50,0:05:54.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}沒有想到我竟然會聽到這兩個女生的談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是什麼花樣啊 土死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.07,0:05:58.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.68,0:06:08.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k127}怎麼女人一碰上買衣服和打電話就沒完沒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好漂亮的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}這麼冷的天還穿超迷你裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}真性感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.27,0:06:26.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是原子筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k272}這會不會是剛才那個姐姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}請留步 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}你掉了東西了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.07,0:06:47.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等等等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:05.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你們在引誘“連續婦女遇襲事件”的嫌疑犯上鉤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.48,0:07:11.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}所以我們才會請佐藤警官打扮成那個樣子的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k139}你們公佈的歹徒身高在150公分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你們看我這身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k115}就應該知道我不可能是歹徒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不不 可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.64,0:07:26.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}您接近佐藤警官的樣子實在是有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的確看不出什麼善意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}我也覺得有點危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.99,0:07:33.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}遭到襲擊的那三位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}在案發當時都打扮得非常誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}除此之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k85}她們就再也沒有其他的共同點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}案發現場又非常淩亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 那三位小姐的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}能不能再讓我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.85,0:07:55.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}第一個遭到攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k137}是這位水谷涼子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.51,0:08:02.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}她是兩星期前的一個夜裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}在十字路口等待綠燈的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k235}突然被人開車從後面追撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}就在她打算下車開始埋怨的時候
