Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k189}我是167公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.75,0:15:12.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}這麼說來 那位社長就非常可疑了
