Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.06,0:18:08.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k263}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蘭
