Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k135}我是指這位小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你也這麼認為啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}是吧是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k123}有點怪對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}也不知道是那裡怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這名被害的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}不知道那裡怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}真要說有什麼不對勁
