Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為那天天氣有點冷的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}那麼 這個姐姐為什麼要穿得這麼單薄
