Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}最近的年輕女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}都是喜歡穿這種薄薄的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.62,0:19:49.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}可是她穿的是件無袖的連身洋裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.74,0:19:50.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就算再怎麼時髦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}這也實在太冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k145}說不定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k115}她原本是在一個很溫暖的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}當時只是去上一下廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k102}很快就要回到原來的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}她原本在很溫暖的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.00,0:20:01.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k104}好比說 像是在車子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.13,0:20:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在車子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k106}這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}第一位與第三位遇害的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}的確都是在下車之後遭到歹徒攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 第四件又發生在停車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}那我就去檢查一下車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k259}好吧 高木老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}你現在立刻就去找第二位受害者確定這件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.90,0:20:31.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.15,0:20:35.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k125}那位社長是歹徒的可能性就降低了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.73,0:20:38.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 這點還很難說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}每次都麻煩你真不好意思 名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}松本警政廳長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}你也到這來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.99,0:20:51.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我說目暮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k107}外面那些媒體記者現在都吵著說這是一起無差別謀殺案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你就快點把這裡的事情結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}明天再重新辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.06,0:21:01.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}就這麼辦吧 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.97,0:21:06.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k163}再說我們現在也還不能確定被害人原本是坐在車上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.68,0:21:07.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}要是真的沒有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.21,0:21:11.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}我下次再化個黑人妝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k299}開車出來試試好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.74,0:21:15.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}我已經說過了 不准你再去引誘歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 請你再讓我們在這裏檢查一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}應該還可以找到什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}而且我有感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.23,0:21:31.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}犯人現在應該還在這附近才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那就隨便你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.41,0:21:37.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目暮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.51,0:21:43.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你該不會是還在意當年的那件案子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.34,0:21:49.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}藏在你那頂帽子下被封印了的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 我早就放下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.14,0:22:05.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.79,0:22:08.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}那就當我問錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.20,0:23:51.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪 那個鞋子根本不合適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.60,0:23:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.00,0:23:57.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}化裝黑人裝的女孩子 是不會穿成那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是說 難道犯人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.10,0:24:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}等一等 難道沒有人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.00,0:24:10.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.40,0:24:14.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}被封印的目暮的秘密(後編）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.70,0:24:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.70,0:24:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}厚底鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}下集是帽子的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.50,0:24:22.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}這是帽子的故事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.80,0:24:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}警官真是很有意思呢
